Package com.example.medirem_project

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddMedicineActivity
    Add medicine activity adds custom medicine to the list which the user has to type in.
    AlertReceiver
    Alert Receiver class receives the alert information and passes it for the notification helper class.
    DatePicker
    DatePicker defines calendar and current day to it https://www.youtube.com/watch?
    MainActivity
    MainActivity holds the calendar and the main functions of this app
    Medicine
    Medicine class holds the information of medicine, like the medicines name, description, date and time.
    MedicineDetailsActivity
    Medicine Details Activity shows the description of the clicked medicine
    NotificationHelper
    NotificationHelper is used to create and manage notification channels.
    SavedMedicine
    SavedMedicine is the singleton class that holds all the saved medicine information
    TimePicker
    Opens a clock where you can choose a time https://www.youtube.com/watch?
